---
// templates/default/components/Features.astro – How it works section
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-16">How it works</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8">
      {[
        { icon: '🏗️', title: 'Multi-tenant architecture', desc: 'Each tenant gets their own branded landing page, served from a shared infrastructure.' },
        { icon: '✏️', title: 'Visual editor', desc: 'Edit content in real time with a live preview powered by the same Astro SSR renderer.' },
        { icon: '⚡', title: 'Instant updates', desc: 'Changes are saved to the API and the preview iframe reloads automatically.' },
      ].map(f => (
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-4 w-full sm:w-72 lg:w-80 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <span class="text-4xl">{f.icon}</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">{f.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500">{f.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
